[2]
Date: Mon 11 Aug 2014
Source: Telegrafonline [edited]
http://www.telegrafonline.ro/1407704400/articol/275970/trei_romani_suspecti_de_antrax.html


At the end of last week, it was announced that there are 2 suspected [cases in] Olt [of] anthrax infection.

Yesterday [10 Aug 2014], another man in the same county was found suspected of having anthrax, leading to 3 the number of potential patients, according to TVR. He was admitted to hospital in Caracal, where there is already another patient. Both were isolated in the Department of Infectious Diseases. Their families have been advised by doctors to come to the hospital for [monitoring]. The 3rd suspect is a woman who has, since last Wednesday [6 Aug 2014], been admitted to a hospital in Pitesti.

